summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning; amending Plat 14E page 60 of the Official Land Use Map to rezone property at 6416 8th Avenue Northeast from Lowrise 3/Residential Commercial (L3/RC) to Neighborhood Commercial 3/40' (NC3/40') and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith. (Petition of ARCO Products Company, c/o Bruce Creager, C.F. 297331.)
